																				{lot.gainLossUsd != null ? fmtGain(lot.gainLossUsd) : '—'}
																			</td>
																			<td class="px-4 py-2 text-center whitespace-nowrap">
																				<span class={`inline-block rounded-full px-1.5 py-0.5 text-[10px] font-semibold ${
																					lot.term === 'long'
